english translation text:
She cries out, O Grandfather;
I have come here with a plea,
I have left Hussain (a.s.) in the desert of Karbala

urdu transliteration text:
Nana Ajeeb Saanaye Hum Par Guzar GayeRanjo Alam Ne Gher Liya Hum Jidhar Gaye..Nana KHUDA Ke Ghar Mai Na Humko Aama MiliBhaai Ne Sheher Chodke Jungle Ki Raah Li..
O Grandfather, we faced strange calamities,
@HujjatELC

Nana Shaheed Ho Gaye Bhaai Ke Jaa Nisaar...Ek Ek Karke Mar Gaye Ashaab E Zee WiqarNana Bala Ke Ban Mai Qayamat Ka Ran PadaaBhaai Se Bhaai Baap Se Beta Bichad Gayaa
Brothers lost brothers, and fathers lost their sons
@HujjatELC

Nana Zameen Karbobala Laal Ho Gayi...QASIM(ASWS) Ki Laash Ghodo Se Paamal Ho Gai...Nana Katake Shaano Ko ABBAS(ASWS) Mar Gaye....Gurbat Mai Bhaaijaan Ko Be Aas Kar Gaye..
Grandfather, Abbas was martyred after his hands were amputated,
@HujjatELC

ZAINAB(ASWS) Jo Roke Karti Thi Qabr E NABI(SAWW) Pe Ben...Tharra Raha Tha Roza E SULTAN E MASHRAKAIN (SAWW)...Bas Khatm  Kar Nisaar Ye Gham Naak DastanRoye Hai Is Alam Mai Zamee Aur Aasmaaaa
O poet please stop narrating this devastating story,
@HujjatELC

Itne Mai Ek Shaami Ne Nana Gazab Kiya...Saidaani Ko Kaneezi Mai Usne Talab Kiya..Hoti Thi Laakh Zillate Hum Dekhte Rahe...Has Haske Taaziyane Sitam Jhelte Rahe
@HujjatELC
We witnessed innumerable insults,
